以下是一个适用于C++项目的常用 `.gitignore` 文件内容：
# 忽略编译生成的文件
*.o
*.obj
*.exe
*.out
*.a
*.so
*.dll
*.lib
*.dylib

# 忽略IDE和构建系统生成的文件
.vs/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
cmake-build-*/
build/
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user
*.suo
*.sdf
*.opensdf
*.pdb
*.idb
*.ilk
*.log
*.tlog
*.lastbuildstate
*.db
*.ipch

# 忽略CMake生成的文件
CMakePresets.json
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CMakeScripts/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile
install_manifest.txt
CTestTestfile.cmake
Testing/

# 忽略依赖目录
deps/
third_party/

# 忽略日志和临时文件
*.log
*.tmp

# 忽略测试相关文件
test_results/
*.gcno
*.gcda
coverage/